  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 300 peasant farmers in Nkoranza</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The National Beekeepers Association will train and supply bee hives  and other beekeeping equipment to 200 women and 100 men from 10 villages in the Nkoranza district to incorporate beekeeping in their farming activities to increase crop yields through pollination and also harvest the honey, beeswax,and other bee products to increase their income and improve their livelihood.We will establish a community honey processing center to process the honey to sell.</narrative>
  </description>
